QuestData.Title: Crabulous Feast
QuestData.Description:
The Forsaken didn't bring any food with them. I think they might be cannibals. At the very least, they don't need to eat!
Teekay and I are going to starve out here! $n, if you're not too busy, could you bring us something to eat?
Maybe some fresh crab?
QuestData.LogDescription: Gather $1oa lumps of crab meat from the Derelict Hexopods.
